{
  "stem": "945.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember for sure, but I would guess that the population was anywhere between 5,000 and 10,000 people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish population, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was a well-known Yiddish-- Yiddish shtetl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Life went on like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this goes approximately into the '35, '36.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in '35, '36, '37, things started to change.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The normal pattern of trying to make a living and working and-- and caring for-- for families and for children started in some way to be influenced by new winds, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm referring, of course, to the political situation that started to develop in Germany, as well as the political situation that started to develop in the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] When the first news started to come out that the Jewish people were being discriminated in Germany, that the Nazis were starting to prosecute Jews simply because they were Jews-- pardon me-- the first opinion at home was that it almost can't be possible.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I particularly remember a little later, a couple of years later, the famous Kristallnacht, when my parents and our neighbors were sitting around a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] radio-- a Telefunken radio.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were listening to the news coming out about the atrocities of the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was just a little boy, but I do remember their expressions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And what they said was, it can't be possible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The German people are not those kind of people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My parents and our neighbors were from the Austrian era.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they remembered the Germans in that time to be civilized and good people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They lived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They respected-- where they lived in Austria, they were respected.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Their religion was respected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Their rights were respected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They served the Kaiser.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They served the Austrian army.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
